race.comment: INTEGRATOR (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.15) at this track behind Ritza Riot in a Other. Has the pace to be prominent. Sure to be about the mark. SLIPPER'S APPEAL (8) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 342m behind Dark Moonshine (20.35) in a Invitation. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Likely to be thereabouts. PIPPA'S HERO (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (19.97) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Gawler. Can improve sharply here. FANTASTIC TOMMY (5) can play a role in the finish without surprising.
